            },
            {
              "type": "span",
              "property": null,
              "children": ". You can also record a video clip of current screen by pressing start recording button."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "br",
      "property": null,
      "children": null
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "property": null,
      "children": "You may locate screenshots and video clips that were taken by the Game Bar in the Videos > Captures folder in File Explorer . These files are saved in the PNG and MP4 formats. Additionally, you may access them through the Game Bar's Gallery by selecting Show my captures > See my captures from the Capture menu, which is located beneath the screenshot and recording buttons."
    },
